        "evidence": "<p dir=\"ltr\"><span>The PEN-FAST Score is calculated by the addition of the selected points:</span><b></b></p>\n<div dir=\"ltr\" align=\"left\">\n<table style=\"width: 100%; height: 386.21875px;\"><colgroup><col style=\"width: 53.7542662116041%;\"><col style=\"width: 24.91467576791809%;\"><col style=\"width: 21.160409556313994%;\"></colgroup>\n<tbody>\n<tr style=\"height: 54px;\">\n<td colspan=\"2\" style=\"height: 54px;\">\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Variable</strong></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"height: 54px;\">\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Point</strong></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 54px;\">\n<td rowspan=\"2\" style=\"height: 108px;\">\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"><strong>F</strong></span><span>ive years or less since reaction</span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"height: 54px;\">\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><span>No</span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"height: 54px;\">\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><span>0</span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 54px;\">\n<td style=\"height: 54px;\">\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><span>Yes</span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"height: 54px;\">\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><span>2</span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 54px;\">\n<td rowspan=\"2\" style=\"height: 116.21875px;\">\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"><b>A</b></span>naphylaxis or angioedema</p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">OR</p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"><strong>S</strong></span>evere cutaneous adverse reaction</p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"height: 54px;\">\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><span>No</span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"height: 54px;\">\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><span>0</span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 62.21875px;\">\n<td style=\"height: 62.21875px;\">\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><span>Yes</span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"height: 62.21875px;\">\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><span>2</span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 54px;\">\n<td rowspan=\"2\" style=\"height: 108px;\">\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"><strong>T</strong></span><span>re